data.name: ToolTip_HoldRender_Modern
data.value: Performs better than the original by batching all segments into one shape, saving dozens, if not hundreds of calls to SkiaSharp. Also fixes the tv-static-looking seams on dense holds.

data.value: Original rendering method that draws holds segment-by-segment. Bad performance, but technically more mature.
